==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|glanc|ing}}

# ''[[intransitive]]:'' To [[look]] [[briefly]] at something
# ''[[intransitive]]:'' To [[strike]] a [[surface]] and be [[deflected]]
# ''[[transitive]]:'' To [[graze]] a surface.

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[vilkaista]] (1), [[pälyillä]] (1)

===Noun===
'''glance'''  (''plural:'' '''[[glances]]''')
# A [[brief]] or [[cursory]] look.
# A [[deflection]].
# A form of [[mineral]] with a [[brilliant]] [[lustre]].

